 class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c005fd22a2caabeef9db12f85953feced0da18f4","tid":58722,"uid":56716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T06:11:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>比大隻仔抱住黎屌兩下就好返架啦</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n邊度有大隻仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n驚屌屌下嘔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你條淫西大火雞，病到都咁鹽濕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n睇熱門嗰個偷拍post睇到濕濕地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7efb60a20ac584c0eac0ef6f8b1f3fb69df5672f","tid":58722,"uid":57695,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T06:11:27.000Z","msg":"渣渣"},{"pid":"043a6eaacf9b51bfa9ebf6bde64e7588768d008c","tid":58722,"uid":56716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T06:11:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>惺咁渣ga</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n身子弱呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n成日都屙嘔肚痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"381b2a062188ca528531a2f679fa581b8e238d2e","tid":58722,"uid":56716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T06:13:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmfMQLfQunty7kxubgFabK6qrH6QdxE679qMbouaCGP5EJ?filename=E682033.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FE682033.jpg&h=21168720&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n象仔你真係日日都食呢款架？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我而家一睇到食物就有啲想嘔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n多數係<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n超級大肥佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n肥佬先正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但你份工好快就會消耗咗碗麵啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab850e9b387bbac2d7d9b70ebe42c3e8bb63300f","tid":58722,"uid":7212,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T06:14:06.000Z","msg":"淨食包會營養不足架喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dff39954a93b679d9a95bb91d055874006bcfcb8","tid":58722,"uid":20963,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T06:14:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\n象仔你真係日日都食呢款架？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我而家一睇到食物就有啲想嘔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n多數係<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n超級大肥佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n肥佬先正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但你份工好快就會消耗咗碗麵啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我成日蛇王<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有入冇出<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eaa4e16960051f2859e9151301e24453e3fbd2fc","tid":58722,"uid":12824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T06:17:21.000Z","msg":"係咁嘔,<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 感冒菌入腸"},{"pid":"05a65aaab03849e223e3634e09c2c916b4fdaada","tid":58722,"uid":12824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T06:17:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係咁嘔,<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 感冒菌入腸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" clas